<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Scrabble Variants & House Rules — Popular Rule Modifications</h1>

<p>Standard Scrabble rules have served players well since 1948, but the game's community has invented dozens of variants that keep things fresh. From lightning-fast Speed Scrabble to the chaotic fun of Clabbers, there's a variant for every mood and skill level. Plus, nearly every family has their own house rules — some brilliant, some controversial.</p>

